<section id="beliefs" class="section beliefs" aria-labelledby="beliefs-title">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section__head">
      <h2 id="beliefs-title">What Christadelphians Believe (In General)</h2>
      <p>A high-level summary of common convictions.</p>
    </header>

    <ul class="beliefs__list">
      <li>There is one God—Father and source of all purpose.</li>
      <li>Jesus is the Son of God, not a co-equal or “God the Son.”</li>
      <li>The dead are not conscious; the hope is resurrection.</li>
      <li>Satan is not usually taught as a supernatural being in Scripture; the word is often an “adversary” or opposition.</li>
      <li>Salvation is through faith in Jesus, grounded in obedience and God’s promises.</li>
      <li>God’s Kingdom will be established on earth, bringing peace and restoration.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
